_sText:
This is "sequel" to trap_catacombs. It's a tighter and smaller version of a traps map which includes even more interesting traps and play on triggers.

The classic "floortrap" traps are still in, and there are some special ones, such as the water trap, a slowly water filled room, the panic button, the yellow corridor, and so on.

This is a definitely good map to add to any fun/custom maps server.
